An ancient riverman~
An ancient riverman is here working to perfect a new boat.
~
A very old man wise in the ways of the rivers stands before you with a toothless grin upon his face.  His hands are worn and caloused from many years of
labor and work upon boats.  He has retired from adventuring now and sells
boats for a living.
~
