mpechoat $n Suddenly the pain hits you with unrimmiting force, causing you toblack out...Mercifully...
mpslay $n
mppurge
mpecho The Riverman throws a flask at $n which breaks and causes his very flesh to dissolve and fall to the floor, leaving behind a puddle of sticky goo.
~
