#11100
Before the Dark Jungle~
You are standing on a lightly-travelled, overgrown path with exits leading to
the north and the southeast.  A dark jungle lies to the north and seems to
beckon you onward.  To the south lies a large hill with its eastern half 
dominated by a gigantic willow tree, making you wonder how a tree could ever
reach such a great size and how long it must have taken.  Farther to the south
you hear the rushing waters of the Khelorn as they tumble by.
~
