Entering the Rapids~
The Khelorn tosses you almost as if you weighed less than a feather here, and
the steep sided banks almost fly by as you struggle to keep from getting
thrown from into the rocks and drowned.  You could attempt to struggle upstream
and out of the rapids but to do so would be a challenged even for the most 
seasoned adventurer, or you could proceed onwards praying that somehow you 
survive this trip throught the whitewaters of the Khelorn.
