#11120
Tumbling Upon the Whitewater~
As you tumble about upon the Khelorn you wonder what foolishness ever provoked
you to make this journey.  Everything you have carried with you is drenched,
and the river's unrelenting will is bringing you close to the breaking point.
The high banks to the north and south offer no hope of a reprieve your only hope
is to proceed upstream to the west or further downstream to the east and hope
that your luck holds out.
~
