#11122
Upon Lake Khelorn~
The river Khelorn flows in from the east and widens into a small lake.  The
lake is very deep, and, although you cannot see to the bottom, is very clean.
The surface is like a mirror due to its solid quartz bottom, causing it to 
reflect back whatever is in the sky above. The lake continues to expand in a
westerly direction, and to the east the river narrows into rapids.
~
