#11124
Crossing Lake Khelorn~
You are near the center of the mirrorlike Lake Khelorn.  To the west the river
Khelorn plows endlessly into the lake, ensuring that it will never run dry. 
To the north there is a dark forest embracing the shoreline, and to the south
