To the east there is a path upon the beach, leading into the eastern marsh.
To the distant west you see the mouth of the Khelorn emptying in the lake.  
To the south, there is a lightly-forested shore that rises quickly into a high
ridge cutting off any attempts to view what lies in that direction.  To the 
north a dark shadowy forest embraces the lake and holds it tightly in its
