the shore a light forest begins and travels upwards to the top of a ridge. To
the northeast, there is a trail leading into the wetlands that lie upon the
southeastern edge of the lake. In the distance, the northern shore is covered
in a thick haze that makes the individual trees of the thick forest surrounding
that end of the lake blur together into one giant green strip.  To the east
