Upon Lake Khelorn~
You are upon the mirrorlike waters of the Khelorn Lake.  Although called a lake
it is more accurately a very wide section of the Khelorn River caused by the
restricting of its flow as it enters a cave system far to the north.  To the
south you see a lightly forested ridge that rises high, and to the southeast
you see a marshy trail that leads to the lands beyond the ridge.  Along the
northern shore is a great dark forest that is covered in a thick haze, and far
to the west you see the mouth of the Khelorn river as it constanly fills the 
lake on its endless journey from the west.
